{"tid":1063664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港媽斥菲傭英文發音不正教壞BB　言語治療師：1歲才會發出有意思單字","createTime":"2019-03-16T02:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T09:04:41.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"929d9def90c2e852f0cc6e4e62485ff0b466c6f3","tid":1063664,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:57:04.000Z","msg":"本港不少父母因工作繁忙，會聘請外傭幫忙照顧小孩。有港媽日前在facebook群組發文吐苦水，指家中的菲傭英文的發音及語法不正確，教壞BB，例如「apple」讀成「啊蒲」，更謂糾正過對方，並為此罵對方亂教一通。帖文一出，網民幾乎一面倒地認為港媽苛刻，指出家傭不是老師。有言語治療師指出，嬰兒6個月大進入牙牙學語的階段，1至3歲口部肌肉和語音仍在發展階段，發音不清屬正常情況。<br />\n該名港媽在facebook群組「外傭僱主必看新聞訊息」發文呻，問是否每位外傭英文也講不好，擔心BB與家中菲傭相處時間多，會學了不正確的發音：<br />\n&quot;其實係咪每個工人（菲）啲accent同grammar都係一擔擔？講真BB對住佢點都多過我地，我已經盡量抽時間去對返BB，講多啲野，真係好擔心會學到佢啲衰野。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n她又指，因為菲傭中英文發音不正確，曾責罵對方，更叫她不懂中文不要亂教：「上次先比我鏟佢一鑊黎，唔識講白話係到亂教。」她指，當菲傭教BB稱呼自己時，教BB「姐姐」讀「車車/啫啫」。其後又舉出教英文的例子：「Apple」讀「啊蒲/april」，「Mango」讀「炆go」，「Bath」讀「but」，<br />\n&quot;仲有好多，多不勝數<br />\n頭先聽到佢socks讀左suck 忍唔住出post&quot;<br />\n<br />\n帖文一出引起網民熱議，有網民指出，家傭的職責不是教英文，「家傭只是做家務，正確教育小孩應請家庭教師。」也有人認為外傭算不錯，「人哋肯同你個仔玩，有興趣同佢傾計，樂觀啲咁諗你係請到好工人」，同時有人指港媽可「尊重工人姐姐口音，欣賞對方願意教自己小朋友」。<br />\n也有人指有口音是正常的，指出「個個地方都有口音」，更反問當初會通過面試：「當時有對答，你應該聽到佢口音唔岩你心水先係喎，點解你又請佢返來嘅？」另有人為發音問題給予建議，「請位英國正宗英文老師全天候睇實姐姐，一錯就糾正佢教到岩先準姐姐同少主對話」。<br />\n基督教靈實協會靈實恩光成長中心言語治療師方奕欣早前接受TOPick訪問時表示，嬰幼兒不同階段有不同的表達能力。1至3歲小朋友口部肌肉和語音仍在發展階段，發音不清屬正常情況。<br />\n6個月大：正式進入牙牙學語階段，但該階段發出的聲音未必有特定意思。<br />\n9個月大：逐漸有意識模仿家長的說話，去表達特定的意思。如發出「ba」表達爸爸或熟識的人，同時嬰兒可能會發出一些如外星話的說話練習發音的技巧。<br />\n1歲：真正發出有意思的單字，如叫得出「爸爸」、「媽媽」、「奶奶」等字詞。<br />\n1歲半起：慢慢掌握到兩個詞語的短句，如「媽媽抱」、「我食」。詞彙發展十分迅速，可能只教導一、兩次，他們已學會一些字詞。<br />\n2歲：開始能夠說稍為完整句字，如我想食麵包，我要去街街；開始發問問題，如說：「邊個？」；詞彙更豐富，懂得簡單形容詞：好多、得意、乖等。<br />\n3歲：句子愈來愈長，如「今日我同媽咪一齊去超級市場」，BB話相對也會少講，取而代之是成人的說話，例如「包包」變成「麵包」，「奶奶」變成「牛奶」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2295000/2295996/worker_thumb_20190315_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2295000%2F2295996%2Fworker_thumb_20190315_S_1024.jpg&h=f50f027d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b971a94cda3522bd6290d04d3962c99797af7721","tid":1063664,"uid":44171,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"去牛津請個英國人黎湊仔麻, 但又係想3千樓下請到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98abcc6f2c07529761c194cd16ec25086880bdb","tid":1063664,"uid":23180,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b971a94cda3522bd6290d04d3962c99797af7721","tid":1063664,"uid":44171,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"去牛津請個英國人黎湊仔麻, 但又係想3千樓下請到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"香港大部人又cheap又要求高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae49914b95ef0adfeaba90d9fc4b3d1b4a78421","tid":1063664,"uid":191352,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa4ba325b2c8931e634a50586b12e428a340a917","tid":1063664,"uid":224533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:06:34.000Z","msg":"港媽咪又係有Chinglish口音"},{"pid":"c5607eb784a1a64c103da9ffa3ea3659f113e585","tid":1063664,"uid":30966,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:07:28.000Z","msg":"請菲傭定請英文老師"},{"pid":"2148d27f4a3c81ccbb16bb8230efeb9d66def4c3","tid":1063664,"uid":241426,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"呢啲就真係「閪客」喇！<br />\n俾得個幾千蚊，要求人地牛津口音，屌佢老味合約有冇寫？呢啲師奶真係香港之光呀！<br />\n我仲認為你影響地區形象添，我係咪都要去投訴呀？屌你老母！"},{"pid":"d404bee1d558413220b4b928c9d785f3f3017c54","tid":1063664,"uid":165510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:10:38.000Z","msg":"自己咁叻自己教呀嘛 又要諗埋啲縮數<br />\n呢啲女人真係肉撚酸"},{"pid":"a24f6002fb3a7fd2df66b15acfd3b6e1a889fea2","tid":1063664,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eae49914b95ef0adfeaba90d9fc4b3d1b4a78421","tid":1063664,"uid":191352,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"咪係囉，工人還工人，補習老師還補習老師，兩份工既人工都唔同啦"},{"pid":"27d5758562f2a357f058abbaf811fd5b799ef3a5","tid":1063664,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:18:31.000Z","msg":"請鬼妹囉on9"},{"pid":"ede7d9b04165e44690f7e1a0b820d2bb0e0841d9","tid":1063664,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:29:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ca446af304fba56cca5b3e8bcd6941d5b71e52d","tid":1063664,"uid":193893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:35:54.000Z","msg":"我覺得工人就係BB既模範，所以已經去信白金漢宮，洽聘英女皇做我new-born daughter既保姆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aede451b75e45ac0300145c759b892a742536cb7","tid":1063664,"uid":79355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"佢自己口音都唔會正得去邊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c6aba2c0520e6be5b42040e4a79b5f968cd34e","tid":1063664,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T08:51:50.000Z","msg":"畀多少少4皮嘢一個月請個英國婆咪冇事"},{"pid":"ca0135c597787cf1e1093a3d049ebc48b61abec6","tid":1063664,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a24f6002fb3a7fd2df66b15acfd3b6e1a889fea2","tid":1063664,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eae49914b95ef0adfeaba90d9fc4b3d1b4a78421","tid":1063664,"uid":191352,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"咪係囉，工人還工人，補習老師還補習老師，兩份工既人工都唔同啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T08:56:31.000Z","msg":"睇嚟你返工係夠膽屌老細吩咐你做工作以外嘅嘢嘅人"},{"pid":"ede02d08fbac97e896580c1b5e0595048b031866","tid":1063664,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"似係嗰媽嘅英文唔掂"},{"pid":"6887903d5a699ba93bbfe3d341ee599da6c18134","tid":1063664,"uid":22231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eae49914b95ef0adfeaba90d9fc4b3d1b4a78421","tid":1063664,"uid":191352,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:04:41.000Z","msg":"其實係想你唔好教佢。。"}]}